      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 46,
      "message": "You need a \"notify\" job that notifies that the job is starting. The call-gerrit-rtdv3-merge will need it. You then need a report-status job that needs both of the other jobs to notify the final outcome of the whole workflow.\n\nLook at the gerrit-ci-management-merge workflow from the reusable workflows for an example.",
